snippet.title: Prince of Persia - The forgotten sands PSP Game play Trailer [Europe]
snippet.description: First look at the PSP version of Prince of Persia The Forgotten Sands. New exclusive powers available for more mind racking puzzles to solve and more powerful ways to defeat enemies!
